title: Exporting Messages

To export one or many ChatGPT conversations:

#Open conversation you would like to export

#At the top of the conversation, click the export button <$macrocall $name="exportButton" 
            exportFilter=<<currentTiddler>>
            lingoBase="$:/language/Buttons/ExportTiddler/" 
            baseFilename=<<currentTiddler>>/>

#Select desired file format (static HTML is suggested)

#If you wish to change the name of the file, open in your folder, right click and click "rename"
